{
  "doc_id": "11540",
  "text": "Inter-rater and intra-rater agreement was analysed with the interclass correlation coefficient (ICC) (two-way mixed model, type absolute agreement), taking into consideration that an ICC of 0-0.2 represents slight agreement, 0.21-0.4 fair agreement, 0.41-0.6 moderate agreement, 0.61-0.8 substantial agreement and 0.81-1 excellent agreement [CITATION_1] .",
